@startuml
hide members
hide methods
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 70
skinparam ranksep 180
skinparam arrowFontSize 20
skinparam classAttributeFontSize 16

class VehicleModel
class ManufactureBom
class ProcessRoute
class PlanningStrategy
class Material
class Process
class ProductionResource
class WorkCalendar
class ProductionOrder
class OrderBomItem
class PlanInfo
class PlanTask
class WorkReport
class IncomingMaterialOrder
class BufferZone

' === 强制分层（隐藏线） ===
VehicleModel -[hidden]down- ManufactureBom
ManufactureBom -[hidden]down- Material
Material -[hidden]down- ProductionOrder
ProductionOrder -[hidden]down- PlanInfo
PlanInfo -[hidden]down- WorkReport

' === 同层对齐（隐藏线） ===
ManufactureBom -[hidden]right- ProcessRoute
ProcessRoute -[hidden]right- PlanningStrategy

Material -[hidden]right- Process
Process -[hidden]right- ProductionResource
ProductionResource -[hidden]right- WorkCalendar

ProductionOrder -[hidden]right- OrderBomItem

PlanInfo -[hidden]right- PlanTask

WorkReport -[hidden]right- IncomingMaterialOrder
IncomingMaterialOrder -[hidden]right- BufferZone

' --- 车型关联 ---
VehicleModel ..> ManufactureBom : 默认BOM
VehicleModel ..> ProcessRoute : 默认工艺路线
VehicleModel ..> PlanningStrategy : 排产策略

' --- 工艺建模 ---
ProcessRoute --> Process : 包含工序
ProcessRoute ..> Material : 适用产品
Process ..> ProductionResource : 可用资源
Process ..> Material : 消耗物料

' --- 订单展开 ---
ProductionOrder --> OrderBomItem : 生成需求明细
OrderBomItem ..> Material : 需求物料
ProductionOrder --> PlanTask : 拆分任务

' --- 排产计划 ---
PlanInfo --> PlanTask : 包含
PlanTask ..> Process : 对应工序
PlanTask ..> ProductionResource : 占用资源
PlanTask ..> WorkCalendar : 日历约束

' --- 执行反馈 ---
WorkReport ..> PlanTask : 关联任务
WorkReport ..> ProductionOrder : 所属订单
WorkReport ..> ProductionResource : 实际资源

' --- 辅助 ---
IncomingMaterialOrder ..> Material : 来料物料
BufferZone ..> ProductionResource : 上下游关联
@enduml
